This repository contains configuration files I'm using on my computer.

You will find here :

awesome
    The Awesome WM

bash*
    Bash config

calcurse
   A calendar

conkyrc
   A system monitor

feh
   An image viewer and cataloguer

mcabber
    A simple Jabber client

mpd
    A Music Player Daemon

nano
    A simple text editor

rtorrent
    A BitTorrent client

screenrc
    A terminal multiplexor

vimrc
    A complex text editor

xinitrc
   My X startup script

install_config
   A script to symlink in place all these config files
